-align: -0.671ex; margin-left: -0.089ex; width:1.259ex; height:2.009ex;" al=
t=3D"{\displaystyle p}"></span> <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Un=
it_vector" title=3D"Unit vector">unit vectors</a>, where the <span class=3D=
"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-i=
nline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://=
