</p><p>Principal component analysis has applications in many fields such as=
 <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Population_genetics" title=3D"Pop=
ulation genetics">population genetics</a>, <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.=
org/wiki/Microbiome" title=3D"Microbiome">microbiome</a> studies, and <a hr=
ef=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Atmospheric_science" title=3D"Atmospher=
ic science">atmospheric science</a>.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-2" class=3D"referen=
ce"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Principal_component_analysis#c=
ite_note-2"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>2<span class=3D"cite-brack=
