-align: -0.671ex; width:5.405ex; height:2.009ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle n\t=
imes p}"></span> data <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Matrix_(math=
ematics)" title=3D"Matrix (mathematics)">matrix</a>, <b>X</b>, with column-=
wise zero <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Empirical_mean" class=3D=
"mw-redirect" title=3D"Empirical mean">empirical mean</a> (the sample mean =
of each column has been shifted to zero), where each of the <i>n</i> rows r=
