=3D"Polar decomposition">polar decomposition</a> of <b>T</b>.
</p><p>Efficient algorithms exist to calculate the SVD of <b>X</b> without =
having to form the matrix <b>X</b><sup>T</sup><b>X</b>, so computing the SV=
