rem" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Karhunen=E2=80=93Lo=C3=A8ve theorem">Ka=
rhunen=E2=80=93Lo=C3=A8ve</a> transform (KLT) of matrix <b>X</b>:
</p><p><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=
