-align: -0.838ex; width:2.972ex; height:2.843ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle (\a=
st )}"></span> holds if and only if <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-mat=
h-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11=
